                "quality_rating": 3
            },
            {
                "comment": "In all honesty, one of the worst professors I have ever had. Her grading methods are absolutely awful and treats the class as an advanced English class for assignments regarding grammar. She gives very little time for people to think of a response when she calls on you. If you do not respond quickly enough she will move on and mark you as absent. ",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 1
            },
            {
                "comment": "Course material is interesting &  she is knowledgeable & enthusiastic. However, her notes on the board are incredibly disorganized & she wings lectures. Also this class causes anxiety as she requires name tents and carries notecards with your image on them- calls on individuals randomly and expects you to know specific info from  long readings.",
                "difficulty_rating": 4,
                "quality_rating": 3
